7.1 If any provision of this Licence is invalid or unenforceable, that shall not affect the validity or enforceability of the remainder of the Licence.

7.2 This Licence shall be governed by the laws of Switzerland. Any dispute arising from or in connection with this Licence will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts of Geneva, Switzerland.

7.3 You may choose to offer, and to charge a fee for, warranty, support, indemnity, or liability obligations to one or more Recipients, provided that you do so on your own behalf, and not on behalf of the Licensor or any Contributor. You must make it clear that any such rights offered by you are without the participation of the Licensor or any Contributor.

